Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不论那是雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Losion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还是下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还是祥和的午后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊  这美丽的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,120分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在干啥
